Sarah Jones has been under house arrest after she was charged in Covington, Kentucky with sexual abuse for allegedly sleeping with a student at the high school where she taught English.

The women's lawyer  Eric Deters told WCPO that both of his clients would accept a deal but refused to give further details. 

The mother and daughter are expected in court on Monday at 9am.

